Package org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer

Class ProbabilisticDoubleInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.ProbabilisticDoubleInterval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ProbabilisticDoubleInterval
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An value representation that is capable of expressing uncertainty. It addresses uncertainty by expressing estimates as intervals and assigning a probability of correctness (in [0, 1]).
    See Also:
